		<title>03POPULATION</title>
		<content>                                       
 The population is spread around in    
 small estates,mostly privately owned. 
 Historically the custom prevailed that
 allowed a person to claim the land if 
 he erected his house in one           
 night.This partially explains why     
 there are so many scattered houses in 
 Minera.                               
 A considerable number of people in    
 Minera speak Welsh,though its use as a
 first language is not prominent.      
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
